summary: I made this for my Archer/Alchemist build.
descriptionHtml:
I made this for my Archer/Alchemist build. barely does magic so I went ahead and lumped scrolls and magic together.  All shouts and powers and together but I haven\'t made the subsists yet. Well, enjoy!
So far its compatible with Titanis super smithing mod.
If you find any miscategorization please let me know and I will fix it. Thanks guys!

Get Categorized Favorites Menu by favmenumodder here:
